</p>
<p>Our first job should be to query for a <code>Genus</code> object. I'll be lazy again and just
type-hint an argument with <code>Genus</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="3e635927bf">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
