<p>That means that its output will be a <code>Genus</code> object, but its input should <em>also</em>
be a <code>Genus</code> object.</p>
<p>Behind the scenes, it will use the getter functions on <code>Genus</code> to pre-fill the form:
like <code>getName()</code>. And everything else is exactly the same. Well, I'll tweak the flash
message but you get the idea:</p>
