<p>Refresh. Change the "Fun fact" to be even more exciting, hit enter, and there it is:</p>
<blockquote><p>Genus updated - you are amazing!</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Edit that Genus again: there's the new fun fact. This is a <em>really</em> cool thing
about the form framework: the new and edit endpoints are <em>identical</em>. The only difference
is that one is passed default data. </p>
<p>So this is great! Except for the template duplication. That's not great still.</p>

    
